title: The Collection
description:
So, I've decided to go through all my CDs. With every artist / band I have in my collection, I am going to post my favourite song by that artist. For example, I have all the T.Hip's albums, but I can still only pick one song! No matter how embarassing me having these CDs are, I gotta suck it up and make it public! (Keep in mind, I never throw out CDs!... with the exception of AFI...) I will post a torrent file at the end of this, featuring all the songs listed!
Lets git r done!
